name: Farks
content: Farks was a Patrolian who lived during the High Republic Era. A friend of the pirate queen Maz Kanata, Farks gave her a vonduun crab skull from Zav Alox which Kanata kept in her castle on Takodana. Later, after an infant Aloxian came into Kanata's care and began wearing the skull, Farks travelled to Takodana on the pirate's request and told her about the origin of the skull and the Aloxians.
